---
title: Burrito-Style Tex-Mex Turkey Tacos with Pico de Gallo & Red Pepper Crema
description: Craving tacos? Daydreaming about burritos? Then let’s taco ‘bout what’s for dinner! Our chefs put together a Tex-Mex-inspired taco-burrito hybrid that’s sure to satisfy. There’s ground turkey and onion simmered with Mexican-style spices, fresh pico de gallo, red pepper crema, and jasmine rice, all piled into steamy-soft tortillas. The best part? You’ll be savoring these beauties in only 25 minutes!
